§ Baahbosa

⸺ by Charles Iliya Krempeaux

In the [[world-18]] //animation// and //fictional world//, **Baahbosa** is one of the [[world-18-characters]].

**Baahbosa** is a very high ranking //member of// and //commander in// the [[serpent-troopers]].

**Baahbosa** is also part of the [[cult-of-usirus]].

**Baahbosa** is a very powerful fighter.

**Baahbosa** is usually completely covered by the [[serpent-trooper-armor]] — and thus to most his identity, and even his lineage, is unknown.
